$interpreted: Jerus: He transformed?

Jerus: No reaction?
If so... everyone, get him!
Jerus: H, have mercy...
Fatima: Stop right there!

Fatima: Huff... puff...
No need... to dirty your hands... for worthless scum like him...
Elio: Miss Fatima, so you guys are safe?
Fatima: Had to run with every muscle available... We're this close to being utterly doomed...
Fatima: Those three brats fainted from the impact of the last explosion. I didn't come out of this totally unscathed either...
Fatima: Elio, what's going on with your appearance...
Fatima: Will the three brats be alright?
Charle: Fortunately, none of them suffered any life-threatening injuries. As long as they get proper treatment and some rest, they should be fine.
Charle: As with you, Elio, the punishment for your unauthorized actions will be determined by me after we return to the Academy.
Fatima: Hey, Elio went through a lot of trouble here too! There's no reason he should be further punished!

Elio: It's fine, Miss Fatima.
Also, thank you, for being willing to help keep my secret.

Fatima: No big deal. Besides, can't really say no after all that desperate pleading you did...
So the feather tribe's wings are retractable...
Fatima: Are you really certain that you're not going to tell Charle about something this major?
Elio: The strings that are connected to this issue are far too complicated and intertwined. I can't drag father into this mess.
Elio: I want to see if I can find the answers on my own...

Elio: (My mother, as well as...)
(My real father... Theodore Carlos...)
